---
// src/components/home/Methodology.astro
---

<section class="py-32 bg-web-background text-web-text relative">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10 bg-[url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/cubes.png')] pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
    
    <div class="text-center mb-24">
      <h2 class="text-sm font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-web-primary mb-4">Nuestro Proceso</h2>
      <h3 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-bold text-white leading-tight">
        Resolución Estratégica
      </h3>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-16 relative">
      <div class="absolute top-4 bottom-4 left-[28px] md:left-1/2 w-[1px] bg-web-secondary -translate-x-1/2"></div>

      <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center gap-8 md:gap-16 group">
        <div class="md:w-1/2 md:text-right order-2 md:order-1 pl-16 md:pl-0">
          <h4 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-web-primary transition-colors">Auditoría Estricta</h4>
          <p class="text-web-text/80 font-light leading-relaxed">Analizamos la documentación y los vacíos legales de su caso con precisión quirúrgica. Sin diagnósticos falsos.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="absolute left-0 md:left-1/2 w-14 h-14 bg-web-secondary border border-web-primary/50 text-white font-bold flex items-center justify-center rounded-full -translate-x-1/2 z-10 group-hover:border-web-accent group-hover:bg-web-accent transition-all">
          01
        </div>
        <div class="md:w-1/2 order-3 md:order-3 hidden md:block"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center gap-8 md:gap-16 group">
        <div class="md:w-1/2 order-2 md:order-3 pl-16 md:pl-0">
          <h4 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-web-primary transition-colors">Estrategia Ofensiva/Defensiva</h4>
          <p class="text-web-text/80 font-light leading-relaxed">Trazamos la ruta de acción (judicial o fiscal) orientada exclusivamente a minimizar sus riesgos y maximizar beneficios.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="absolute left-0 md:left-1/2 w-14 h-14 bg-web-secondary border border-web-primary/50 text-white font-bold flex items-center justify-center rounded-full -translate-x-1/2 z-10 group-hover:border-web-accent group-hover:bg-web-accent transition-all">
          02
        </div>
        <div class="md:w-1/2 order-3 md:order-1 hidden md:block"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center gap-8 md:gap-16 group">
        <div class="md:w-1/2 md:text-right order-2 md:order-1 pl-16 md:pl-0">
          <h4 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-web-primary transition-colors">Ejecución y Control</h4>
          <p class="text-web-text/80 font-light leading-relaxed">Mantenemos un rol activo en la ejecución de la estrategia, manteniéndolo informado de cada avance procesal.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="absolute left-0 md:left-1/2 w-14 h-14 bg-web-secondary border border-web-primary/50 text-white font-bold flex items-center justify-center rounded-full -translate-x-1/2 z-10 group-hover:border-web-accent group-hover:bg-web-accent transition-all">
          03
        </div>
        <div class="md:w-1/2 order-3 md:order-3 hidden md:block"></div>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>